1. Java Persistence API Inheritance
    - JPA Inheritance Strategies: Имплементира се чрез javax.persistence.Inheritance анотацията;
    - Стратегиите за мапване се използват за мапване на entities към базата;
        * A single table per class hierarchy;
        * A table per concrete entity class;
        * "Join" strategy - mapping common fields in a single table.

2. Table Relations
    - One to One Relationships (Shampoos - Labels);
    - One to Many and Many to One Relationships (Shampoos - Batches);
    - Many to Many Relationships (Shampoos - Ingredients);
    - Self Referencing Relationships (Employee - Employee with field manager);